                              <section> <div class="headerimg" style="background-image: url('https://zermatterhof.ch/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/hotel-zermatt-zermatterhof-skipiste-1450x521.jpg')"> <div> <div class="inner "> <p class="sub-title">This is how winter is fun</p><p class="title">Skiing in Zermatt</p> </div> </div> </div></section><section> <article class="text"> <h1 class="title_icon">Matterhorn ski weeks</h1><h2 class="title_main">The definitive way to enjoy the winter</h2><p class="georgia">After a long day’s skiing, return to be pampered by the team at the Grand Hotel Zermatterhof. Après-ski, convivial meals in mountain restaurants and perhaps a shopping trip along Zermatt’s Bahnhofstrasse are all also integral parts of the winter sports experience.</p> </article></section><section> <div class="twocolumns"> <div class="inner"> <img src="https://zermatterhof.ch/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/hotel-zermatt-zermatterhof-matterhorn-und-sternenhimmel.jpg" alt="Matterhorn under a starry sky" srcset="https://zermatterhof.ch/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/hotel-zermatt-zermatterhof-matterhorn-und-sternenhimmel-750x403.jpg 750w, https://zermatterhof.ch/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/hotel-zermatt-zermatterhof-matterhorn-und-sternenhimmel-768x413.jpg 768w, https://zermatterhof.ch/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/hotel-zermatt-zermatterhof-matterhorn-und-sternenhimmel-1450x779.jpg 1450w, https://zermatterhof.ch/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/hotel-zermatt-zermatterhof-matterhorn-und-sternenhimmel-150x81.jpg 150w, https://zermatterhof.ch/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/hotel-zermatt-zermatterhof-matterhorn-und-sternenhimmel-1600x860.jpg 1600w, https://zermatterhof.ch/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/hotel-zermatt-zermatterhof-matterhorn-und-sternenhimmel-1152x619.jpg 1152w, https://zermatterhof.ch/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/hotel-zermatt-zermatterhof-matterhorn-und-sternenhimmel-300x161.jpg 300w" sizes="(max-width: 1450px) 100vw, 1450px"> <div class="columns"> <div class="content"><p>You stay <strong>seven nights at the Grand Hotel Zermatterhof. </strong></p><p><strong>The Matterhorn Ski Weeks package also includes:</strong></p><ul><li>7 day skipass, ski rent und ski lesson</li><li>Transfer to and from Zermatterhof and Zermatt station in our horse-drawn carriage or electric bus on the day of your arrival and departure</li><li>Welcome drink</li><li>Generous breakfast buffet</li><li>Mineral water and soft drinks from the minibar</li><li>Tea and coffee machine and fresh fruit</li><li>Use of the spa, i.e. unlimited access to the pool, steam bath, saunas, ice grotto and gym</li><li>Wireless Internet in your room and in all public areas</li></ul><p><strong>Available </strong>in <strong>December</strong> (30.11. – 21.12.2019), in <strong>January/February</strong> (11.01. – 01.02.2020) and in <strong>March</strong> (21.03. – 28.03.2020).</p><p><strong>Rates: </strong>from CHF 1951.00 per person in a double room</p><h2 class="title_regular remove_space">Book now!</h2><p>Phone <span class="yext-field yext-mainPhone "><a class="call" href="tel:0041279666600">+41 27 966 66 00</a></span> or <a href="mailto:reservation@zermatterhof.ch">reservation@zermatterhof.ch</a></p></div> <div class="content"><p><strong>Six days of group skiing lessons:</strong> Certified local ski instructors will show you how to get maximum enjoyment out of your skiing. The course takes place right on the piste, starting on Sunday morning and continuing up to the end of the day on Friday.</p><p><strong>Seven-day ski pass:</strong> gives you access to 360 kilometres of runs in the Zermatt-Cervinia area in Switzerland and Italy.</p><p><strong>Seven-day ski pass:</strong> normally valid from Sunday until Saturday. Would you prefer to start skiing right from the day you arrive? In that case your ski pass will be valid from Saturday until Friday.</p><p><strong>Seven-day ski hire:</strong> you will be putting the very latest VIP skis from Zermatt’s sports shops through their paces.</p></div> </div> </div> </div></section>                          </main>
        
